      "content": "DONE: task_file param added to delegate_task.\n\nFiles changed:\n- `src/mcp-server.ts`: Added `task_file?: boolean` to `delegate_task` inputSchema. Handler: when true, calls `startActivity(null)` to get an activityId, writes brief to `.synapse/tasks/<activityId>.md`, sends a short pointer message to the worker. Normal path unchanged.\n- `.synapse/SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md`: Added note after step 1 explaining `task_file: true`, when to use it, and the worker instruction to `Read` the file.\n- `.gitignore`: `.synapse/` already covers task files — no change needed.\n\nBuild: `tsc` clean.",
